-- Shares of Turkey's Bank Asya jump 11 pct, reversing initial losses
-- By Seda Sezer
-- Thu Sep 18, 2014 03:26AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 18 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkey's Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS>, an Islamic finance institution, surged 11 percent to 0.71 lira ($0.32) on Thursday, reversing an initial slide of 11 percent at the opening.

